reviewText: Would love to get this on DVDs have 1 & 2 on DVDs but can't find 3. Have all 3 on vhs but dvd is better. Get some in stock and I know they will go fast

I have been waiting to buy this movie on dvd for years, I have it on vhs, I love the Stepfather movies " we just need some order around here!!!" I like his little tanties in the basement!!! very entertaining!!!
